title: The Dolphin
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Local pub offering traditional British pub food, including changing vegetarian/vegan options marked on the board -- might be dishes such as bubble & squeak with mushrooms, thyme roast tomato and sesame tofu; vegan sausages with mustard mash and gravy, or a vegan roast on a Sunday. Food served til 9pm except Sunday til 6pm.
